          </div>
          <div class="card-body d-flex flex-column">
            <p class="card-body-text">Modular Compression & Decompression Algorithms</p>
            <p class="card-body-text">Similar to JPEG algorithms</p>
            <p class="card-body-text">Written in C</p>
            <a class="btn btn-secondary mt-auto" href="https://github.com/john-odonnell/img_compress">GitHub</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="project-column col-lg-4 col-md-6 col-sm-12 d-flex align-items-stretch">
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-header">
            <h4>Tweet Reader</h4>
          </div>
          <div class="card-body d-flex flex-column">
            <p class="card-body-text">Displays Tweets from a given Data Set with navigation options</p>
            <p class="card-body-text">Implements a Circular Doubly Linked List to order Tweets by time of day</p>
            <p class="card-body-text">Written in Python</p>
            <a class="btn btn-secondary mt-auto" href="https://github.com/john-odonnell/csc_212/tree/master/assignments/assignment2">GitHub</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

