          <div class="card-header">
            <h4>Tetris Clone</h4>
          </div>
          <div class="card-body d-flex flex-column">
            <p class="card-body-text">Uses pygame library to implement graphics and event handling</p>
            <p class="card-body-text">Object-Oriented Modular Design</p>
            <p class="card-body-text">Written in Python</p>
            <a class="btn btn-secondary mt-auto" href="https://github.com/john-odonnell/tetris">GitHub</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="project-column col-lg-4 col-md-6 col-sm-12 d-flex align-items-stretch">
