          <div class="card-header">
            <h4>Image Rotation Tool</h4>
          </div>
          <div class="card-body d-flex flex-column">
            <p class="card-body-text">Implements two 2D array structures: Linear and Blocked</p>
            <p class="card-body-text">Each has strength with different rotations based on portions of the structures loaded into registers</p>
            <p class="card-body-text">Written in C</p>
            <a class="btn btn-secondary mt-auto" href="https://github.com/john-odonnell/csc_411/tree/master/locality">GitHub</a>
          </div>
        </div>
